DataProfile.Name: Explore Data
DataProfile.SQLExpression: "N$10069" AS ( SELECT ATTR, DATA_TYPE, NULL_PERCENT, DISTINCT_CNT, DISTINCT_PERCENT, MODE_VALUE, AVG, AVG_DATE, AVG_TS_TZ, MEDIAN_VAL, MEDIAN_DATE, MEDIAN_TS_TZ, MIN, MAX, STD, VAR, SKEWNESS, KURTOSIS, HISTOGRAMS FROM OUTPUT_8_24)

Aggregation.Name: Aggregate
Aggregation.SQLExpression: "N$10005" as (SELECT t0."CUST_ID", t0."AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM", t0."QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG" FROM (SELECT "CUST_ID", CAST(COLLECT(DM_NESTED_NUMERICAL(ID1, "AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM")) AS DM_NESTED_NUMERICALS ) "AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM", CAST(COLLECT(DM_NESTED_NUMERICAL(ID1, "QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG")) AS DM_NESTED_NUMERICALS ) "QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG" FROM (SELECT "CUST_ID", ("PROD_ID") ID1, SUM("AMOUNT_SOLD") "AMOUNT_SOLD_SUM", AVG("QUANTITY_SOLD") "QUANTITY_SOLD_AVG" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} GROUP BY "CUST_ID", (("PROD_ID")) ) GROUP BY "CUST_ID") t0 )

Join.Name: Join
Join 1

Apply.Name: Cluster Assignments
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10014" as (SELECT CLUSTER_ID("CLUS_KM_1_4" USING *) "CLUS_KM_1_4_CLID", CLUSTER_PROBABILITY("CLUS_KM_1_4" USING *) "CLUS_KM_1_4_PROB", "CUST_ID" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Apply.Name: Likely customers
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10052" as (SELECT PREDICTION_PROBABILITY("CLAS_NB_1_4", 1 USING *) "CLAS_NB_1_39_PROB_1", PREDICTION_DETAILS("CLAS_NB_1_4", 1, 3 ABS USING *) "CLAS_NB_1_39_PDET" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

ModelDetails.Name: Model Details
ModelDetails.SQLExpression: "N$10012" as ( SELECT CAST('DMUSER' AS VARCHAR2(128)) as "MODEL_SCHEMA", CAST('CLAS_NB_1_4' AS VARCHAR2(128)) as "MODEL_NAME", VV.PARTITION_NAME as "PARTITION_NAME", VV.TARGET_NAME as "TARGET_ATTRIBUTE_NAME", VV.TARGET_VALUE as "TARGET_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE", VP.PRIOR_PROBABILITY as "PRIOR_PROBABILITY", VV.ATTRIBUTE_NAME as "ATTRIBUTE_NAME", VV.ATTRIBUTE_SUBNAME as "ATTRIBUTE_SUBNAME", VV.ATTRIBUTE_VALUE as "ATTRIBUTE_VALUE", VV.CONDITIONAL_PROBABILITY as "CONDITIONAL_PROBABILITY" FROM DMUSER.DM$VVCLAS_NB_1_4 VV INNER JOIN DMUSER.DM$VPCLAS_NB_1_4 VP ON NVL(VV.PARTITION_NAME, 0) = NVL(VP.PARTITION_NAME, 0) AND VV.TARGET_NAME = VP.TARGET_NAME AND VV.TARGET_VALUE = VP.TARGET_VALUE )
